name: Egg White Breakfast Cups  🥩
description: These protein-packed breakfast cups are perfect for meal prep or busy mornings. Made with fluffy egg whites, fresh spinach, and juicy tomatoes, they're a healthy and delicious way to start your day.
instructions: Preheat the oven to 350˚F (180˚C). Grease 6 cups of a muffin tin with nonstick spray.
Divide the spinach evenly among the prepared muffin cups.
Dice the tomato and divide among the muffin cups, then pour in the egg whites. Season with salt and pepper.
Bake for 15 minutes, or until the whites have set.
